126
00:09:08,875 --> 00:09:12,875
Back when I was running Monstro,
a lot of shit went down.

127
00:09:12,958 --> 00:09:15,416
Everybody was glaring at me
with that fire in their eyes,

128
00:09:15,500 --> 00:09:16,791
know what I mean?

129
00:09:16,875 --> 00:09:19,583
