131
00:09:23,333 --> 00:09:26,333
We'd known each other
ever since we were kids.

132
00:09:26,416 --> 00:09:28,000
He just understood me.

133
00:09:29,583 --> 00:09:32,500
He was the only one
I could tell everything to.

134
00:09:32,583 --> 00:09:34,458
Even the embarrassing shit.

135
00:09:37,166 --> 00:09:40,375
And always, he would
lend me a sympathetic ear.

136
00:09:42,958 --> 00:09:45,166
What's that look on your face?

137
00:09:45,250 --> 00:09:46,666
Forget it.

138
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:47,708
It's nothing.

139
00:09:47,791 --> 00:09:49,750
You got something
to say, spit it.

140
00:09:49,833 --> 00:09:53,375
From what I've heard, I get
the feeling he's not so great.

141
00:09:53,458 --> 00:09:55,666
Honestly, I bet Hiroshi
wasn't even listening to you

142
