I'll see her again.

171
00:11:23,458 --> 00:11:26,833
Which means she must
know where he is, too then.

172
00:11:28,458 --> 00:11:30,541
--are saying both the freight
train derailment, and the bar

173
00:11:30,625 --> 00:11:33,583
shootout that preceded it, may
be part of an ongoing series

